                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-224-off1265 t18321129-224-cd1266"></join>, 1 pocket-book, value 2s., and I bill of exchange, value 15l., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18321129-224-victim1965" type="victimName">
